net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser

Class BinaryCsvParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser.BinaryCsvParser
  • Deprecated. 
    Use ParserManagerByteLine.getInstance().get(ICsvParserIds.EXTENDED_BASIC_CSV_PARSER) instead !!!!

    public class BinaryCsvParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for working with delimited records where the Delimiter is provided as a byte. As such it will
    • Extract a field from an array of bytes
    • Set a field in an Array of bytes
    • Get the starting position of a field in an array of Bytes
    • Count the number of fields
    Version:
    0.68
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
